The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. For more info, please see http://comtrade.un.org/db/mr/rfGlossaryList.aspx

docs.description: Trade in Glass And Glassware - Uruguay. This data employs the subheadings of the original Harmonized System (HS1992). The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. For more info, please see http://comtrade.un.org/db/mr/rfGlossaryList.aspx

The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. docs.name: Trade in Footwear and Gaiters Products - Trinidad and Tobago
docs.description: Trade in Footwear and Gaiters Products - Trinidad and Tobago. This data employs the subheadings of the original Harmonized System (HS1992). The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. For more info, please see http://comtrade.un.org/db/mr/rfGlossaryList.aspx

docs.description: Trade in Footwear and Gaiters Products - United Arab Emirates. This data employs the subheadings of the original Harmonized System (HS1992). The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. For more info, please see http://comtrade.un.org/db/mr/rfGlossaryList.aspx

docs.name: GDP - Current Prices, US Dollars - Mali
docs.description: Mali GDP by Type of Expenditure at current prices - US dollars. The National Accounts Main Aggregates database is produced and maintained by the Economic Statistics Branch of the United Nations Statistics Division (UNSD), with input from the UNSD, international organizations, and the national statistical agencies of more than 200 countries.  The database consists of a complete and consistent record of the main National Accounts of each UN member state, from 1970 onwards.  Records are based on official country data reported to the UNSD, supplemented with estimates for any years and countries with incomplete or inconsistent information.  The database is updated in December of each year. For more about the National Accounts Main Aggregates database, see http://unstats.un.org/unsd/snaama/introduction.asp.  To see country-specific metadata, see <a href=http://unstats.un.org/unsd/snaama/metasearch.asp?letter=M>http://unstats.un.org/unsd/snaama/metasearch.asp?letter=M.

The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962.
